pid":"21c713df74748d1a09040bc067829b0a1d068101","tid":1637616,"uid":60200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T06:29:33.000Z","msg":"其實會社已經安排好了, 香港唯一出路就係靠美國, 要俾美國有藉口去保護香港, 香港人而家可以做既就係盡快令美國通過香港人權及民主法案, 同盡快將所有港元換做美金, 跟住調出國, 其他野基本上冇乜用"},{"pid":"51bb1a04dc84df0f4e3475bce7c3108d148a6da4","tid":1637616,"uid":304935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T06:31:02.000Z","msg":"大家都知道西方人好<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">重視言論自由</span></span><br />\n所以,大家麻煩<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">煲大火箭隊莫雷發表既言論</span></span><br />\n既然依家中國共產黨企到咁硬, 咁我地就<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">煲大佢!</span></span><br />\n將中國共產黨變成對人地既<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">國家安全威脅!</span></span><br />\n等全世界人都覺醒<br />\n將中國共產黨視為對西方文明既威脅!!!!<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聯合抗共, 將全世界人民聯合起來, 反抗暴政!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">United We Stand, Divided We Fall!!!!!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">仲有電競選手果單! 將呢兩件事變成西方憲政危機同威脅!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n傳開去, 感謝手足!<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d22866d3101bd931a003ed08007bf511aff705bc","tid":1637616,"uid":60200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T06:31:20.000Z","msg":"而家香港最有力係打金融戰, 因為香港有錢, 而中共而家正正好需要錢, 所以提款或將美金匯出國正正傷到佢要害"},{"pid":"e22f95046b704f43fc83a3715e2e2c3